===Best coach=== *'''Decided by:''' Players and coaches
Fellow national team captains and coaches vote for who they want to be crowned best coach of the year.<ref name="voters"/> BSWW reveal a shortlist of the three coaches with the most votes prior to the ceremony.{{ref|Note1|[Note]}} On the awards night, the winner of the award with the most votes of the three is revealed as the best coach of the year.
