===Rising star award=== *'''Decided by:''' BSWW panel of experts
Experts at BSWW decide which young player (age range undefined) will be crowned best in the world for the year.<ref name="voters"/> On the awards night, the winner of the award is revealed. No preliminary shortlist is disclosed. {| class="wikitable" !Year !width=160|Winner !width=160|Team !DOB & age when awarded |- |rowspan="2"|<center>'''2014'''<ref name="twentyfourteen"/></center> |- |Noël Ott || {{beachsoccer|SUI}} || {{Birth date and age2|2014|11|07|1994|01|15|df=y}} |- |rowspan="2"|<center>'''2015'''<ref name="twentyfifteen"/></center> |- |Bernardo Martins || {{beachsoccer|POR}} || {{Birth date and age2|2014|11|07|1989|12|29|df=y}} |- |rowspan=2|<center>'''2016'''<ref name="twentysixteen"/></center> |- |Rodrigo da Costa || {{beachsoccer|BRA}} || {{Birth date and age2|2016|11|05|1993|08|16|df=y}} |- |rowspan="2"|<center>'''2017'''<ref name="twentyseventeen"/></center> |- |Boris Nikonorov || {{beachsoccer|RUS}} || {{Birth date and age2|2017|11|04|1989|04|03|df=y}} |- |rowspan="2"|<center>'''2018'''<ref name="twentyeighteen"/> |- |Mohammad Moradi || {{beachsoccer|IRN}} || {{Birth date and age2|2018|11|10|1996|08|31|df=y}} |}
===Best Five=== *'''Decided by:''' Players and coaches
Fellow national team captains and coaches vote for the five players that they believe, combined, form the best team of the year,<ref name="voters"/> similar to the [[FIFPro#FIFA FIFPro World XI|FIFA World XI]] award in [[association football]]. On the awards night, the five winners of the award with the most votes are revealed as the ''Best Five''. {| class="wikitable" !Year !width=170|Players !width=120|Team !width=120|Position |- |rowspan="6"|<center>'''2014'''<ref name="twentyfourteen"/></center> |- |Dona|| {{beachsoccer|ESP}} || Goalkeeper |- |[[Ilya Leonov]]|| {{beachsoccer|RUS}} || Defender |- |Ozu Moreira|| {{beachsoccer|JPN}} || Defender |- |[[Bruno Xavier]]|| {{beachsoccer|BRA}} || Midfielder |- |Llorenç Gomez|| {{beachsoccer|ESP}} || Forward |- !colspan=4| |- |rowspan="6"|<center>'''2015'''<ref name="twentyfifteen"/></center> |- |Jonathan Torohia || {{beachsoccer|TAH|name=Tahiti}} || Goalkeeper |- |Heimanu Taiarui || {{beachsoccer|TAH|name=Tahiti}} || Defender |- |Ozu Moreira|| {{beachsoccer|JPN}} || Defender |- |Bruno Xavier|| {{beachsoccer|BRA}} || Midfielder |- |[[Madjer]] || {{beachsoccer|POR}} || Forward |- !colspan=4| |- |rowspan=6|<center>'''2016'''<ref name="twentysixteen"/></center> |- |[[Elinton Andrade]] || {{beachsoccer|POR}} || Goalkeeper |- |Ozu Moreira|| {{beachsoccer|JPN}} || Defender |- |Bruno Xavier|| {{beachsoccer|BRA}} || Midfielder |- |[[Madjer]] || {{beachsoccer|POR}} || Forward |- |[[Dejan Stankovic (beach soccer)|Dejan Stankovic]] || {{beachsoccer|SUI}} || Forward |- !colspan=4| |- |rowspan="6"|<center>'''2017'''<ref name="twentyseventeen"/></center> |- |Mão || {{beachsoccer|BRA}} || Goalkeeper |- |Bruno Xavier || {{beachsoccer|BRA}} || Defender |- |Mauricinho || {{beachsoccer|BRA}} || Midfielder |- |Noël Ott || {{beachsoccer|SUI}} || Forward |- |Mohammad Ahmadzadeh || {{beachsoccer|IRN}} || Forward |- !colspan=4| |- |rowspan="6"|<center>'''2018'''<ref name="twentyeighteen"/> |- |Elinton Andrade || {{beachsoccer|POR}} || Goalkeeper 