{{Infobox video game |title = Skidz |image = |caption = |developer = [[Core Design]] |publisher = [[Gremlin Graphics]] |designer = |engine = |released = [[1990 in video gaming|1990]] |genre = [[sports game|Sports]] |modes = |platforms = [[Amiga]], [[Atari ST]] }}
'''''Skidz''''' is a [[skateboarding]] and [[BMX]] themed [[sports game|sports]] video game [[video game developer|developed]] by [[Core Design]] for the [[Amiga]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hol.abime.net/1962|title=Skidz : Hall Of Light The database of Amiga games|work=abime.net}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lemonamiga.com/games/details.php?id=971|title=Skidz, Skids - Amiga Game / Games - Download ADF, Cheat - Lemon Amiga|work=lemonamiga.com}}</ref> and [[Atari ST]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.atarimania.com/game-atari-st-skidz_11231.html|title=Atari ST Skidz : scans, dump, download, screenshots, ads, videos, catalog, instructions, roms|work=atarimania.com}}</ref> It was released in 1990 and [[video game publisher|published]] by [[Gremlin Graphics]].
